cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.DS, cs.SE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with first-order logic and its application in safety games. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the synthesis of strategies to enforce safety, which is a common problem in AI. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper deals with the verification of parametric systems such as network protocols and conference management systems. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses techniques for abstraction and refinement to synthesize FO-expressible strategies. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also relevant as the paper deals with the verification of software-defined networks and multi-agent workflows.
